  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"color: inherit;letter-spacing: undefinedpx;font-weight: normal;font-family: SF Pro SC,SF Pro Text,SF Pro Icons,PingFangSC-Light,PingFang SC,Helvetica Neue,Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;margin: 0 6px;margin-bottom: 6px;padding: 6px 6px;border: 0px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 1);background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0);border-radius: 0px;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <div style=\"text-align: center!important;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;display: block;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n    <p style=\"display: block;margin: 8px 0px 0px;box-shadow: none;border-radius: 0px;line-height: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100010522\" alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.42407407407407405\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;border: none;padding: 0px;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b8b79e92&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FfbRX0iaT8EgfgvssBPEib8PK0iaRR1m1qVS61IibEaeCpXkk8vX0ibZfEsjCsrE5YxXEB4bicGq6z6vJ4WtMaqkficKFA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Djpeg%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: normal;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: rgb(100, 106, 115);font-size: 16px;line-height: 2;margin: 8px 0px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(100, 106, 115);font-family: &quot;SF Pro SC&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">前几天 Nano Banana Pro 玩疯了吧，有没有想过什么时候视频模型也能有类似的能力。</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: normal;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: rgb(100, 106, 115);font-size: 16px;line-height: 2;margin: 8px 0px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(100, 106, 115);font-family: &quot;SF Pro SC&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">现在，他来了。可灵发布了 O1，一个大一统的视频、图像生成和编辑工具，支持在一个界面和流程中完成你需要的全部视频图片编辑和生成工作。</span></span></span></p>\n   <div style=\"border:1px solid rgb(254,212,164);border-radius:8px;padding:12px 14px;place-items:flex-start;color:inherit;display:flex;margin-top:16px;margin-bottom:16px;text-align:left!important;\">\n    <div style=\"width: 100%;margin-top: 8px;\">\n     <p style=\"width: 100%;margin: 8px 0px 0px;color: inherit;font-weight: normal;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;font-size: 16px;line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;font-family: &quot;SF Pro SC&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">总结一下这次更新内容：</span></span></span></p>\n     <ul style=\"list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n      <li>\n       <p style=\"width: 100%;margin: 8px 0px 0px;color: inherit;font-weight: normal;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;font-size: 16px;line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;font-family: &quot;SF Pro SC&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">统一多模态视频大模型，把参考生视频、文生视频、首尾帧、内容增删与风格重绘等任务融合，一站式完成从生成到修改。</span></span></span></p>\n      </li>\n      <li>\n       <p style=\"width: 100%;margin: 8px 0px 0px;color: inherit;font-weight: normal;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;font-size: 16px;line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;font-family: &quot;SF Pro SC&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">支持图片、视频、主体与文字的多模态输入，直接用自然语言进行精细编辑，无需遮罩或关键帧。</span></span></span></p>\n      </li>\n      <li>\n       <p style=\"width: 100%;margin: 8px 0px 0px;color: inherit;font-weight: normal;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;font-size: 16px;line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;font-family: &quot;SF Pro SC&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">通过多视角主体与参考素材，保持角色、道具、场景的特征稳定与镜头间一致性，确保连贯画面。</span></span></span></p>\n      </li>\n      <li>\n       <p style=\"width: 100%;margin: 8px 0px 0px;color: inherit;font-weight: normal;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;font-size: 16px;line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;font-family: &quot;SF Pro SC&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">自由组合参考与指令，覆盖运镜、动作、镜头延展等复杂玩法。</span></span></span></p>\n      </li>\n      <li>\n       <p style=\"width: 100%;margin: 8px 0px 0px;color: inherit;font-weight: normal;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;font-size: 16px;line-height: 2;\"><span style=\"font-weight: bold;font-family: &quot;SF Pro SC&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;color: rgb(0, 0, 0) !important;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight:normal;\">可生成约 3–10 秒的自由叙事镜头，灵活控制节奏与镜头长度。</span></span></span></p>\n      </li>\n     </ul>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: normal;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: rgb(100, 106, 115);font-size: 16px;line-height: 2;margin: 8px 0px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(100, 106, 115);font-family: &quot;SF Pro SC&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">老规矩，先来看一个藏师傅关于这次相对重要的视频编辑能力和多图参考能力的演示视频：</span></span></span></p>\n   <p class=\"channels_iframe_wrp\" nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n   <div></div>\n   <p></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: normal;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: rgb(100, 106, 115);font-size: 16px;line-height: 2;margin: 8px 0px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(100, 106, 115);font-family: &quot;SF Pro SC&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">然后我会对这次新增的一些能力进行测试，同时大概教大家一下这个模式应该如何使用。</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: normal;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: rgb(100, 106, 115);font-size: 16px;line-height: 2;margin: 8px 0px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(100, 106, 115);font-family: &quot;SF Pro SC&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">进到可灵页面，你就会注意到左侧新增了一个非常显眼的图标，用了这个后面那几个界面你基本就用不着了。</span></span></span></p>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center!important;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;display: block;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n    <p style=\"display: block;margin: 8px 0px 0px;box-shadow: none;border-radius: 0px;line-height: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100010523\" data-ratio=\"0.6925925925925925\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;border: none;padding: 0px;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=d2569f41&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FfbRX0iaT8EgfgvssBPEib8PK0iaRR1m1qVSsicQ9eqIcnibicgENCmQmAib2WHkUnfordOyFqCLBhbDoCicRNVa0AXbLOA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: normal;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: rgb(100, 106, 115);font-size: 16px;line-height: 2;margin: 8px 0px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(100, 106, 115);font-family: &quot;SF Pro SC&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">进来以后就会发现下方的提示词输入框位置集成了非常多的选项，下方用来切换视频和图片生成的基础操作，比如时间比例等，上方的几个胶囊按钮主要用来控制输入内容的类型。</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: normal;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: rgb(100, 106, 115);font-size: 16px;line-height: 2;margin: 8px 0px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(100, 106, 115);font-family: &quot;SF Pro SC&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">比如图片主体参考这里他就会出现、视频、图片、主体三个输入项，当然你可以删除图片或者主体，只用文本操作。</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: normal;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: rgb(100, 106, 115);font-size: 16px;line-height: 2;margin: 8px 0px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(100, 106, 115);font-family: &quot;SF Pro SC&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">然后首尾帧这个输入项就会变成首帧和尾帧，这个我们就熟悉了，不过提示词也需要对首尾帧进行标注。</span></span></span></p>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center!important;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;display: block;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n    <p style=\"display: block;margin: 8px 0px 0px;box-shadow: none;border-radius: 0px;line-height: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100010519\" data-ratio=\"0.39351851851851855\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;border: none;padding: 0px;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=81c9a07d&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FfbRX0iaT8EgfgvssBPEib8PK0iaRR1m1qVS3DBQkk2qH0ynowsibDqVhWoA4z54U4Ue7hCmeDMiazTZ4d96V4CviazpA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: normal;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: rgb(100, 106, 115);font-size: 16px;line-height: 2;margin: 8px 0px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(100, 106, 115);font-family: &quot;SF Pro SC&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">我们先来看一下最基本的通过文本进行视频编辑，你只需要上传需要编辑的视频，然后在提示词输入框输入提示词的时候在指代素材那里@ 对应的素材就行。</span></span></span></p>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center!important;margin-left: auto;margin-right: auto;display: block;margin-bottom: 0px;\">\n    <p style=\"display: block;margin: 8px 0px 0px;box-shadow: none;border-radius: 0px;line-height: 0px;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img alt=\"Image\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100010521\" data-ratio=\"0.40370370370370373\" style=\"display: inline-block;max-width: 100%;height: auto;border-radius: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;margin-right: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 0px;border: none;padding: 0px;\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0972e2df&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FfbRX0iaT8EgfgvssBPEib8PK0iaRR1m1qVSOrr52YibK054cqZBibv8M9YDUJ9g1FXS941WdWEOn4byhzpva0MSalJw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: normal;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: rgb(100, 106, 115);font-size: 16px;line-height: 2;margin: 8px 0px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(100, 106, 115);font-family: &quot;SF Pro SC&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">然后你就看到你的视频已经被修改了，比如这里我说的是穿上黑色风衣和带上墨镜，可以看到服饰的质感还是非常不错的，干周围环境融合的也很好，窗台的阳光照在衣服上的高光也有。</span></span></span></p>\n   <p style=\"font-weight: normal;font-family: inherit;word-break: break-all;min-height: 20px;color: rgb(100, 106, 115);font-size: 16px;line-height: 2;margin: 8px 0px 0px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;color: rgb(100, 106, 115);font-family: &quot;SF Pro SC&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Text&quot;, &quot;SF Pro Icons&quot;, PingFangSC-Light, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;white-space: pre-wrap;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\">可以看到嘴型和运动都可以迁移，所以你可以将 O1 当做数字人模型使用。</span></span></span></p>\n   <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n   